title: Judas Priest - New York City soundboard 1979-11-04
description:
Judas Priest

New York City, NY, 1979/11/04

The Palladium, New York City, NY, US
November 4, 1979
FM broadcast

01 - Hell Bent for Leather
02 - Delivering the Goods
03 - Running Wild
04 - The Ripper
05 - Beyond the Realms of Death
06 - Diamonds and Rust
07 - White Heat, Red Hot
08 - Sinner
09 - The Green Manalishi
10 - Victim of Changes
11 - Genocide
12 - Starbreaker
13 - Take on the World
14 - Tyrant

Audio source and quality:
FM broadcast, very good to excellent quality. Originally broadcast on the New York-based WNEW radio station.

Special features:
At the start of Take on the World, Rob Halford claims that 1980 will be the year of heavy metal.
